<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Special+Gothic+Expanded+One&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/logofinal.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
  <title>Moodmatch</title>

  <style>
        body {
            opacity: 0;
            animation: fadeIn 2.5s forwards;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .project-title {
            font-size: 70px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            font-family: 'Special Gothic Expanded One', Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-left: 10%;
        }

        .project-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-family: 'Special Gothic Expanded One', Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: left;
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-top: 30px;
            max-width: 80%;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .project-video {
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            max-width: 80%;
        }

        .project-video video {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid #ff0000;
        }

        .project-image {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            max-width: 80%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .figma-embed {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            width: 80%;
            height: 600px;
            border: 2px solid #ff0000;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .back-button {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header', { activePage: 'portfolio' }) %>
    <%- include('partials/videobg') %>

    <div class="container-fluid">
        <h1 class="project-title">moodmatch</h1>
        
        <div class="project-description">
            we've all been there - scrolling endlessly trying to pick a movie. i designed<br>
            this figma mockup for an app that fixes that. just tell it how you're feeling,<br>
            and it'll match you with the perfect film. feeling sad? happy? angry? whatever<br>
            your vibe is, moodmatch has got you covered. no more wasting half your night<br>
            just deciding what to watch.
        </div>

        <!-- Replace the URL below with your Figma prototype embed link -->
        <iframe class="figma-embed" 
                src="https://embed.figma.com/proto/ATEHLVEyt6VCqPuZCB6JjF/C218-FA-24015581?page-id=1%3A3&node-id=21-157&viewport=231%2C428%2C0.1&scaling=scale-down&content-scaling=fixed&embed-host=share" 
                allowfullscreen>
        </iframe>

        <div class="back-button">
            <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-outline-light">back to portfolio</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>